1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:11,340
No? Then why did you
throw away my flowers?

2
00:00:12,780 --> 00:00:15,220
Because you didn't respect
our agreement.

3
00:00:19,220 --> 00:00:20,979
I've never treated what we have

4
00:00:20,980 --> 00:00:22,740
as just a contract.

5
00:00:30,780 --> 00:00:36,430
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

6
00:00:37,710 --> 00:00:43,170
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

7
00:00:44,290 --> 00:00:49,610
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

8
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:56,590
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

9
00:01:01,420 --> 00:01:02,700
It's boiling.

10
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:09,599
=Echoes of Gang City=

11
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:10,859
=Episode 16=

12
00:01:10,860 --> 00:01:14,100
(By Reason, By Fairness, By Law,
Everything Is on Your Side)

13
00:01:19,020 --> 00:01:20,660
Wow, it smells great.

14
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:25,620
Shen Gu,

15
00:01:27,420 --> 00:01:28,780
about Su Mei,

16
00:01:30,420 --> 00:01:31,540
thank you.

17
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:40,020
I should've told you earlier.

18
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:50,020
Here.

19
00:01:50,700 --> 00:01:52,420
Try

20
00:01:52,820 --> 00:01:54,660
the fish maw
and matsutake mushroom chicken soup.

21
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,380
Careful, it's got.

22
00:02:18,540 --> 00:02:20,460
It's really good.

23
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:22,540
Have more.

24
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:24,980
How are you so good at cooking?

25
00:02:33,620 --> 00:02:35,540
When I was abroad,

26
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,980
I missed the taste of Gang City

27
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:43,220
and the people here.

28
00:02:56,020 --> 00:03:00,539
Looks like Wanxin won't be able
to have dinner with me as often anymore.

29
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:03,220
You didn't look like this

30
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:05,060
when you were pushing them together.

31
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:09,540
It finally feels real

32
00:03:09,740 --> 00:03:13,259
that my granddaughter is married.

33
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:15,460
I'll spend more time with you.

34
00:03:17,940 --> 00:03:19,780
There's another soup.

35
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:23,620
Li, come and sit.

36
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:25,900
Sit. Let's eat.

37
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:28,419
Do we still have that bajiu

38
00:03:28,420 --> 00:03:30,860
we brought back from Shen City?

39
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:36,140
You can only have half a glass.

40
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:38,940
Alright, half a glass.

41
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:40,140
Get the bajiu.

42
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:47,140
You two are teaming up
to trick me, huh?

43
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:48,899
Didn't you say

44
00:03:48,900 --> 00:03:52,340
the most dangerous place
is the safest place?

45
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:54,739
Li,

46
00:03:54,740 --> 00:03:56,700
let's toast to Mr. Xu.

47
00:03:57,340 --> 00:03:58,019
Mr. Xu, here.

48
00:03:58,020 --> 00:04:00,740
Wishing you health and happiness.

49
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:02,260
Health and happiness.

50
00:04:02,340 --> 00:04:03,340
Cheers.

51
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:23,640
(Xu Wanxin)

52
00:04:25,770 --> 00:04:27,510
What's up?

53
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:30,340
From today on,

54
00:04:31,700 --> 00:04:33,660
I'm officially living with Shen Gu.

55
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:34,940
What?

56
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:36,460
You're living together?

57
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:38,980
Xu Wanxin,

58
00:04:39,660 --> 00:04:40,980
that's great.

59
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:43,980
You like each other,
and the misunderstandings are cleared.

60
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:45,339
You're adults.

61
00:04:45,340 --> 00:04:47,580
That's how it should be.

62
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:50,180
Yes, but I...

63
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,020
Want to have a round?

64
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:53,980
What?

65
00:04:55,620 --> 00:04:56,860
Miss Song,

66
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:58,260
you can't rush

67
00:04:58,540 --> 00:05:00,459
things like that.

68
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:01,819
What are you talking about?

69
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:03,220
When did I even say?

70
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:04,540
Ah?

71
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:05,819
What did I say?

72
00:05:05,820 --> 00:05:07,540
What are you thinking?

73
00:05:09,820 --> 00:05:10,699
Alright.

74
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:13,339
Just follow your heart.

75
00:05:13,340 --> 00:05:15,140
I have no objections.

76
00:05:15,300 --> 00:05:18,340
Honestly, Shen Gu
seems like a decent guy.

77
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:20,659
That's it. I'm going back to my game.

78
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:22,020
We'll talk when we meet. Bye.

79
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,260
Song Xi!

80
00:05:28,660 --> 00:05:31,619
Did you know

81
00:05:31,620 --> 00:05:32,940
Wanxin moved in with Shen Gu?

82
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:36,220
What is that?

83
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:38,819
It's going to rain.

84
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:41,060
Quick. Let's have one more round.

85
00:05:42,940 --> 00:05:44,060
You

86
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:45,459
are done for.

87
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:47,660
Come on.

88
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,089
Alright.

89
00:05:59,090 --> 00:06:00,340
I'll be fine from here.

90
00:06:00,460 --> 00:06:01,860
Thank you for dinner.

91
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:04,860
I'm homeless tonight.

92
00:06:05,020 --> 00:06:05,940
Also,

93
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:08,020
I don't feel like going back
to be the victim again.

94
00:06:08,620 --> 00:06:10,340
I've got filming tomorrow.

95
00:06:11,420 --> 00:06:12,419
Good night,

96
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:14,220
homeless man.

97
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:18,780
Good night.

98
00:06:22,020 --> 00:06:24,300
I really am homeless now.

99
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:44,440
(Lawyer Fang)

100
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:24,770
♪The clouds hide the faint light
behind them♪

101
00:08:25,740 --> 00:08:29,870
♪A lonely bench on the street corner♪

102
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:34,220
♪Where all feelings come to rest♪

103
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:39,609
♪In the night sky, the moon's trail♪

104
00:08:39,610 --> 00:08:43,599
♪Stitches up and soothes my sorrow♪

105
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:46,479
♪The courage to get close to you♪

106
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:50,110
♪Drives away my hesitation♪

107
00:08:50,830 --> 00:08:53,079
♪Fate turns and brings us together♪

108
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:55,069
♪I search my memories with all my might♪

109
00:08:55,070 --> 00:08:57,979
♪Love catches me off guard♪

110
00:08:57,980 --> 00:08:59,679
♪You, in the album♪

111
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:03,000
The number you've dialed
is currently unavailable.

112
00:09:05,950 --> 00:09:09,659
♪The world suddenly has meaning♪

113
00:09:09,660 --> 00:09:14,200
♪Through the pouring rain, I found you♪

114
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:16,389
♪In the space of our embrace♪

115
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:20,740
♪Stars spill across the sky♪

116
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:30,920
♪Stars spill across the sky♪

117
00:10:03,740 --> 00:10:05,299
You finally decided to pick up.

118
00:10:05,300 --> 00:10:07,139
Is your phone for decoration?

119
00:10:07,140 --> 00:10:09,780
Do you know how many missed calls
you have?

120
00:10:11,100 --> 00:10:13,300
It was a heavy downpour.

121
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:18,020
My pillow was at your place.

122
00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:19,139
I couldn't sleep

123
00:10:19,140 --> 00:10:21,260
without my pillow. You know that.

124
00:10:22,820 --> 00:10:24,699
Come and get it today.

125
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:25,980
That's better for both of us.

126
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:29,859
Shen Gu, I'm not a stray.

127
00:10:29,860 --> 00:10:32,140
I have a home in Gang City, okay?

128
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:05,820
Morning.

129
00:12:06,140 --> 00:12:07,140
Morning.

130
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:18,500
Is there anything you can't do?

131
00:12:20,980 --> 00:12:23,300
You'll find out slowly.

132
00:12:26,980 --> 00:12:28,100
Try it.

133
00:12:53,460 --> 00:12:56,380
I'll give you a ride to work.

134
00:13:24,420 --> 00:13:25,859
What?

135
00:13:25,860 --> 00:13:27,780
Are you thinking of kissing me
in the car again?

136
00:13:33,180 --> 00:13:35,180
I was drunk. I don't remember.

137
00:15:29,010 --> 00:15:34,810
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

138
00:15:36,090 --> 00:15:41,890
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

139
00:15:42,610 --> 00:15:47,970
♪You turn and look back at me♪

140
00:15:49,090 --> 00:15:54,610
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

141
00:15:55,450 --> 00:16:01,090
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

142
00:16:02,370 --> 00:16:07,850
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

143
00:16:08,970 --> 00:16:14,290
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

144
00:16:15,450 --> 00:16:21,250
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

145
00:16:21,650 --> 00:16:28,610
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

146
00:16:28,730 --> 00:16:34,410
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

147
00:16:35,090 --> 00:16:41,449
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

148
00:16:41,450 --> 00:16:44,329
♪The promise we made♪

149
00:16:44,330 --> 00:16:48,009
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

150
00:16:48,010 --> 00:16:54,609
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

151
00:16:54,610 --> 00:17:01,010
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

152
00:17:01,410 --> 00:17:07,729
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

153
00:17:07,730 --> 00:17:12,850
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

154
00:17:13,330 --> 00:17:16,330
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
